AI USAGE AND THINKING PROCESS


Throughout this assignment, I used AI primarily as a teacher and guide to help me understand terminology, clarify concepts, and structure my answers. For each question, I first tried to grasp the ideas myself, then consulted AI to fill gaps in my knowledge or explain unclear terms. I selectively incorporated AI suggestions when they aligned with my understanding and were important enough to mention. I verified everything with external sources, especially YouTube lectures, to ensure accuracy and avoid misunderstandings. AI helped me organize and expand my informal notes into polished responses, though I ignored suggestions that seemed incorrect or confused. I mostly used ChatGPT, and at the end I compared my answers with Gemini to see overlapping feedback. Overall, AI acted as a reliable stepping stone, providing explanations or uncovering solutions even when web sources were insufficient, while I remained in control of the final content.to parts.